### Environment Variables

#### [MODIFY] [.env.example](file:///h:/nodejs-tester/dockerstackds2api/.env.example)

Thêm section mới cho Tinyauth và cập nhật section CADDY AUTH:

```ini
# ================================================================
#  TINYAUTH — Session-based auth gateway (replaces Caddy basic_auth)
# ================================================================
# Auth users in format: user:bcrypt_hash (comma-separated for multiple)
# Generate hash with:
#   docker run --rm ghcr.io/steveiliop56/tinyauth:v5 tinyauth hash -p "YourPassword"
# Example: admin:$2a$14$abc123...
TINYAUTH_AUTH_USERS=admin:$2a$14$replace-this-with-a-real-bcrypt-hash

# Secret key for signing session cookies (32+ chars random string)
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
TINYAUTH_SECRET=replace-with-random-hex-string-64-chars

# Session expiry in seconds (default: 604800 = 7 days)
TINYAUTH_AUTH_SESSION_EXPIRY_SEC=604800
```

---

### Cloudflared — Thêm auth subdomain

#### [MODIFY] [config.yml](file:///h:/nodejs-tester/dockerstackds2api/cloudflared/config.yml)

```diff
  ingress:
+   - hostname: auth.dockerstackds2api.dpdns.org
+     service: http://caddy:80
    - hostname: dockerstackds2api.dpdns.org
      service: http://caddy:80
```

