### Environment Variables — Thêm Cloudflare hostname

#### [MODIFY] [.env.example](file:///h:/nodejs-tester/dockerstackds2api/.env.example)

Thêm hostname/service cho auth vào danh sách Cloudflare Tunnel:
```diff
  CLOUDFLARED_TUNNEL_HOSTNAME_6=deploy.${DOMAIN}
+ CLOUDFLARED_TUNNEL_HOSTNAME_7=auth.${DOMAIN}

  CLOUDFLARED_TUNNEL_SERVICE_6=http://caddy:80
+ CLOUDFLARED_TUNNEL_SERVICE_7=http://caddy:80
```

